name: Ilulu (Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Maid)
description:
Trigger word: ilulu \(maidragon\)

Recommended weight: 0.8-1.0

Useful descriptions: pointy ears, low twintails &| twintails, colored tips, red eyes | orange eyes, slit pupils, sharp teeth, yellow horns, dragon tail & dragon girl, shortstack | petite

Character can be generated without additional descriptions just fine, but in case you don't get what you want try using them in your prompt.

  • v2-Epoch11: should better draw her twintails and horns in cases where it doesn't. Updated Data Set: added some missing poses tags, "dragon girl" for pictures where there is "dragon tail", and removed Hair Length and Hair Color (with exception of "colored tips").

  • Epoch8: may better depict the character, but may start losing prompt details.

  • Epoch5: may follow original image better, but may not get some character features as good.

This lora was trained on 80 different pictures of the character with 3 repeats. I was trying to train it on many different models and in the end, between Anything-v3 and NAI, decided to land on Anything-v3 as it seemed to produce better results. Data with her dragon hands seems to have made Lora worse, so I decided to exclude them. All images shown were used with different models at either strength 0.8 or 1.0.

The models used for preview images are: MeinaMix v8, Grapefruit v4.0, Color Box Model, DualPersonality - Normal Line, Animelike 2.5D, GuaMix3;
